<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>About me</h3>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "me.jpg", width:"100%", alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <hr>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="skill">
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-blue"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div> 
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolore tenetur, ipsum repellendus, ipsam itaque, fugiat ab assumenda iusto eum nulla vitae id necessitatibus recusandae impedit odit quasi quia, reiciendis laborum nihil voluptates?</p>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolore tenetur, ipsum repellendus, ipsam itaque, fugiat ab assumenda iusto eum nulla vitae id necessitatibus recusandae impedit odit quasi quia, reiciendis laborum nihil voluptates?</p>
        <p>
          <button class="btn btn-primary"
           type="button"
           data-toggle="collapse"
           data-target="#jobHistory"
           aria-expanded="false"
           aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job history
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-primary"
           type="button"
           data-toggle="collapse"
           data-target="#education"
           aria-expanded="false"
           aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
          <div id="jobHistory" class="collapse">
            <div class="card card-body">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-body">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="education" class="collapse">
            <div class="card card-body">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-body">
              Scholl 2
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
